# Ryan Realty Design System

**Read `docs/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` for the full specification.** These are the enforced rules.

## Tokens Only — No Hardcoded Values

Every visual property uses a CSS custom property from `app/globals.css`.
No raw hex colors. No raw pixel spacing. No hardcoded font names.

## Fonts

- Display/headlines: `var(--font-display)` → Amboqia Boriango (self-hosted)
- Body/UI: `var(--font-body)` → AzoSans (self-hosted)
- Never load any other font. Never `font-weight: 700` on headlines.
- `h1`, `h2`, `h3` automatically get display font via globals.css selector.

## Colors — Use Semantic Tokens

```
--color-primary: #102742        (navy)
--color-cream: #F0EEEC          (background)
--color-cta: #D4A853            (gold buttons/accents)
--color-cta-hover: #C49843
--color-text-primary: #1A1410
--color-text-secondary: #6B6058
--color-text-muted: #A09890
--color-bg: #F0EEEC
--color-bg-subtle: #FAFAF9
--color-bg-white: #FFFFFF
--color-border: var(--color-border-cream)  (#E2DDD8)
--color-success: #22C55E
--color-warning: #F59E0B
--color-error: #EF4444
```

**NEVER use Tailwind color utilities** like `bg-zinc-*`, `text-zinc-*`, `border-zinc-*`, `bg-emerald-*`, `bg-amber-*`, `text-red-*`, `bg-blue-*`.
Always use e.g. `bg-[var(--color-primary)]` or `text-[var(--color-text-primary)]`.

**Legacy aliases exist** (`--brand-navy`, `--accent`, `--brand-cream`) — do NOT use in new code. Use `--color-primary`, `--color-cta`, `--color-cream` instead.

## Spacing (4px grid)

```
--space-1: 0.25rem (4px)    --space-6: 1.5rem (24px)
--space-2: 0.5rem (8px)     --space-8: 2rem (32px)
--space-3: 0.75rem (12px)   --space-12: 3rem (48px)
--space-4: 1rem (16px)      --space-16: 4rem (64px)
```

Never use Tailwind arbitrary values like `p-[24px]`.

## Radius

```
--radius-btn: 6px       --radius-card: 12px
--radius-input: 8px     --radius-modal: 16px
```

Use e.g. `rounded-[var(--radius-sm)]` or `rounded-[var(--radius-card)]`. Never bare `rounded-xl` or `rounded-lg`.

## Shadows

```
--shadow-subtle   --shadow-medium   --shadow-strong
```

Never use Tailwind `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`, etc.

## Components

- **Buttons**: Use `.btn-cta` class or match its token pattern. Min height 44px.
- **Cards**: Use `.card-base` class. Hover: `translateY(-4px)` + `--shadow-medium`.
- **Header**: Solid `bg-primary text-white`, sticky. No glass/transparency.
- **Skeletons**: `.skeleton` class for loading states.

## Mobile-First

- Base styles target mobile. Add `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:` for larger screens.
- Grids: `grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px on all interactive elements.
- Every data-heavy page needs a `loading.tsx` with skeleton UI.

## Animations

All animations must include `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)` override.
Already defined animations: see `.animate-*` classes in `globals.css`.

## Brand Voice (copy in components)

- No hyphens or colons in user-facing copy
- Never: "stunning", "nestled", "boasts", "don't miss", "won't last", "must see", "exclusive", "unparalleled", "world-class", "exquisite", "once in a lifetime"
- Authentic, genuine, transparent. No pandering. No over-inflating anything. Direct and honest.
- State facts, mention tradeoffs honestly. Write like a neighbor, not a salesperson.
- Optimistic but grounded. Genuinely excited about what makes a place great, without manufacturing hype.
- CTAs must be specific: "See All Caldera Springs Listings" not "Learn More"
